                     <interp inst="t18760918-393-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18760918-393-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Unlawfully having counterfeit coin in his possession with intent to utter it.</rs>
